						<summary>

						<p>This is an incomplete inscription, recording probably the purchase of some land by the <hi rend="italic">Rudragaṇapperumakkaḷ</hi> who managed the affairs of the temple of Mūlasthānam-Uḍaiya-Paramasvāmi at Pēriṅgūr, from a shepherd of the place for 5 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold.</p>						

						</summary>
